{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T08:20:11.9317855+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-flash-latest\", \"tool\": \"final_profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"c9f4aa77-d63b-4458-9714-044b7497fb45\", \"session_id\": \"bdf3d0fd-3dbe-4ee0-9e28-bd622bf16cee\", \"response_id\": \"M6j5advUJJr-qtsPvOjYeA\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"M6j5advUJJr-qtsPvOjYeA\", \"created_at\": 1777969203, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-flash-latest\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='M6j5advUJJr-qtsPvOjYeA', status='incomplete', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"title\\\": \\\"You are Belle!\\\",\\\\n  \\\"description\\\": \\\"You are Belle, the intellectual dreamer who finds more life in the pages of a book than in the gossip of a small town. This outcome fits you perfectly because you prioritize the inner world of the mind and the heart over superficial noise. When you chose to spend your Saturday afternoon curled up with a thick book in a quiet library corner, you signaled a soul that values depth and quiet contemplation. Like Belle, you aren\\\\'t just looking for an escape; you are looking for a world that matches the vastness of your imagination, refusing to settle for a provincial life when there is so much more to learn and discover.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour greatest strength lies in your unique perspective and your ability to see potential where others see only a beast or a dead end. You thrive on the compliment that you see the good in people that no one else does, which speaks to a profound emotional intelligence. This isn\\\\'t just optimism; it is a deliberate choice to look beneath the surface. When a friend comes to you with a problem, you don\\\\'t offer quick fixes. Instead, you listen carefully and ask gentle questions to help them reframe their reality. You are a natural mediator and a visionary who understands that the most clever solutions often come from studying the history of a problem rather than rushing into a reactive choice.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nThere is a fascinating tension in your personality between your thirst for adventure and your deep respect for order. While you crave a life that matches your imagination, you also believe that rules and traditions exist for a reason, choosing to follow them even when they feel restrictive. This suggests a grounded sense of honor and a commitment to protecting your family above all else. You are not a rebel for the sake of being loud; you are a principled individual who moves with intention. Your growth edge lies in balancing this respect for tradition with your need for personal expansion, ensuring that your loyalty to the old ways doesn\\\\'t keep you trapped in a story that has become too small for you.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nIn your day-to-day life, this profile manifests as a quiet but unshakable confidence. You are the person who sits with a problem and trusts that the right move will reveal itself, a trait that brings immense stability to those around you. Lean into your intellectual curiosity and your ability to find beauty in the unconventional. However, watch out for the tendency to retreat too far into', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"incomplete\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=889, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=889), output_tokens=1486, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=988, text_tokens=498), total_tokens=2375, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": 