{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:29.853518+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Miles Morales\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"Miles Morales embodies the spirit of a new generation of heroes, balancing immense power with everyday struggles. You possess a deep sense of responsibility and a unique blend of creativity and empathy.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You are Miles Morales, a hero who understands that great power comes with great responsibility, but also with the everyday challenges of being a teenager. You\\\\'re constantly navigating the intricate web of school, family, and friendships, all while secretly shouldering the weight of protecting your city. This duality defines you, making you incredibly relatable and a beacon of hope for those around you. You connect deeply with others, understanding their struggles and always putting their well-being first, even when it means making personal sacrifices. You often find creative solutions to problems, whether it\\\\'s through your unique powers or your artistic flair, always striving to make a difference in a way that feels authentic to you. Despite your growing confidence, you sometimes grapple with imposter syndrome, questioning if you\\\\'re truly worthy of the mantle you carry. However, it\\\\'s precisely this introspection and your unwavering empathy that make you such a compelling hero. Your biggest pitfall can be taking on too much, driven by your strong sense of duty. Learning to lean on your support system and accepting help is crucial for your long-term success. Ultimately, you represent the idea that anyone, regardless of their background, can rise to the occasion and become a hero in their own right, inspiring others along the way.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1085, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=759, text_tokens=326), total_tokens=1306, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:29.852833Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aazxBOi6mtkPoZa1sAE', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Miles Morales\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"Miles Morales embodies the spirit of a new generation of heroes, balancing immense power with everyday struggles. You possess a deep sense of responsibility and a unique blend of creativity and empathy.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You are Miles Morales, a hero who understands that great power comes with great responsibility, but also with the everyday challenges of being a teenager. You\\\\'re constantly navigating the intricate web of school, family, and friendships, all while secretly shouldering the weight of protecting your city. This duality defines you, making you incredibly relatable and a beacon of hope for those around you. You connect deeply with others, understanding their struggles and always putting their well-being first, even when it means making personal sacrifices. You often find creative solutions to problems, whether it\\\\'s through your unique powers or your artistic flair, always striving to make a difference in a way that feels authentic to you. Despite your growing confidence, you sometimes grapple with imposter syndrome, questioning if you\\\\'re truly worthy of the mantle you carry. However, it\\\\'s precisely this introspection and your unwavering empathy that make you such a compelling hero. Your biggest pitfall can be taking on too much, driven by your strong sense of duty. Learning to lean on your support system and accepting help is crucial for your long-term success. Ultimately, you represent the idea that anyone, regardless of their background, can rise to the occasion and become a hero in their own right, inspiring others along the way.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)], 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': 'auto', 'tools': [], 'top_p': None, 'max_output_tokens': None, 'previous_response_id': None, 'reasoning': None, 'status': 'completed', 'text': {}, 'truncation': None, 'usage': ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), 