{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:30.3084585+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Alana\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"Alana is a fiercely independent spirit, always ready for adventure and unafraid to speak her mind. She navigates complex relationships and challenging circumstances with sharp wit and unwavering determination.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"Alana is defined by her fierce independence and unwavering resolve. She possesses a pragmatic outlook on life, often cutting through emotional noise to address the core issue at hand. While she may appear guarded, her actions consistently demonstrate a deep, protective loyalty towards those she cares about, even if she struggles to articulate it verbally.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYou tend to thrive in dynamic, high-stakes environments, preferring direct action and tangible results over abstract discussions. Your sharp wit and sarcastic humor serve as both a defense mechanism and a way to connect with others, though it can sometimes be misinterpreted. You value honesty and authenticity above all else, and you have little patience for pretense or manipulation.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nHowever, your strong will can sometimes manifest as stubbornness, making it difficult for you to back down even when it might be beneficial. You may struggle with vulnerability, often preferring to shoulder burdens alone rather than asking for help, which can lead to isolation. Your quick temper, while often justified, can sometimes alienate those who don\\\\'t understand your underlying motivations.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1169, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=887, text_tokens=282), total_tokens=1390, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:30.307700Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36adHzBPCyqtsPpuSXyQ8', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Alana\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"Alana is a fiercely independent spirit, always ready for adventure and unafraid to speak her mind. She navigates complex relationships and challenging circumstances with sharp wit and unwavering determination.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"Alana is defined by her fierce independence and unwavering resolve. She possesses a pragmatic outlook on life, often cutting through emotional noise to address the core issue at hand. While she may appear guarded, her actions consistently demonstrate a deep, protective loyalty towards those she cares about, even if she struggles to articulate it verbally.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYou tend to thrive in dynamic, high-stakes environments, preferring direct action and tangible results over abstract discussions. Your sharp wit and sarcastic humor serve as both a defense mechanism and a way to connect with others, though it can sometimes be misinterpreted. You value honesty and authenticity above all else, and you have little patience for pretense or manipulation.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nHowever, your strong will can sometimes manifest as stubbornness, making it difficult for you to back down even when it might be beneficial. You may struggle with vulnerability, often preferring to shoulder burdens alone rather than asking for help, which can lead to isolation. Your quick temper, while often justified, can sometimes alienate those who don\\\\'t understand your underlying motivations.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)], 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': 'auto', 'tools': [], 'top_p': None, 'max_output_tokens': None, 'previous_response_id': None, 'reasoning': None, 'status': 'completed', 'text': {}, 'truncation': None, 'usage': ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1169, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=887, text_tokens=282), total_tokens=1390, cost=None), 'user': None, 'store': None}, 'event': 'llm.raw_response.received', 'level': 'info', 'logger': 'app.services.llm_service', 'timestamp': '2026-05-05T15:30:30.307700Z'}\\\">\", \"_from_structlog\": true}"}
