{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:30.3662938+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"V\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are a mysterious and charismatic revolutionary, driven by a profound desire for freedom and justice. You challenge oppressive systems with unwavering resolve, inspiring others through grand gestures and intellectual discourse.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You embody the spirit of revolution, a mysterious figure dedicated to dismantling oppressive regimes and awakening the populace to the power of individual freedom. Your actions are not merely destructive; they are carefully orchestrated performances designed to ignite thought and inspire change, driven by a deep-seated belief in justice and the inherent rights of humanity. You are a symbol, a force for radical transformation.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour approach is often theatrical and symbolic, utilizing grand gestures, literature, and art to convey your message and challenge the status quo. You possess a keen intellect, capable of intricate planning and philosophical debate, often preferring to work from the shadows, allowing your deeds to speak louder than any personal revelation. You value ideas and principles above all else, seeing them as the true weapons against tyranny.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nWhile your charisma and conviction can rally others to your cause, your methods can sometimes be extreme, leading to isolation or a single-minded pursuit of your goals. You might struggle with the personal cost of your ideals, often sacrificing individual comfort or connection for the greater good. Nevertheless, your legacy is one of profound impact, leaving an indelible mark on those you touch and the world you strive to reshape.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=219, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=219), output_tokens=1088, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=782, text_tokens=306), total_tokens=1307, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:30.365588Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36afC6BNGKqtsP7JK6sQE', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"V\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are a mysterious and charismatic revolutionary, driven by a profound de