{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:30.8486487+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Scott Pilgrim\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You\\\\'re a charming slacker with a heart of gold, often finding yourself in epic battles for love. Life\\\\'s a video game, and you\\\\'re just trying to level up.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You embody the spirit of a charming slacker, a bass player in a garage band whose life often feels like a retro video game. You\\\\'re inherently good-hearted, but your path is frequently complicated by a tendency to avoid responsibility and a somewhat naive approach to relationships. When love strikes, it hits hard, often leading you into fantastical confrontations that require you to literally fight for your affections.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour days are typically filled with band practice, hanging out with friends, and navigating the complexities of your romantic life. You have a knack for getting into trouble, especially when it involves the past relationships of those you care about. While you might initially try to take the easy way out, deep down you possess a strong sense of loyalty and a desire to do the right thing, even if it means facing down a league of formidable exes.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nOne of your biggest challenges is emotional maturity. You can be a bit self-absorbed and prone to procrastination, often needing a significant external push to confront your own shortcomings. Learning to take accountability for your actions and truly understand the impact you have on others is a continuous journey for you.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nUltimately, you are a character defined by growth. Despite your initial flaws and the often absurd situations you find yourself in, you possess an undeniable charm and a genuine desire to evolve. Your journey is about learning to fight for yourself, not just for love, and discovering the hero within that can conquer not only evil exes but also personal insecurities.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1256, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=879, text_tokens=377), total_tokens=1477, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:30.847816Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36afaYBP2BqtsP_Nrf2A8',