{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:31.4084978+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36aYT8BIOfqtsPhYHQsAU\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36aYT8BIOfqtsPhYHQsAU\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aYT8BIOfqtsPhYHQsAU', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Marjane Satrapi\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are a keen observer with an unyielding spirit, navigating complex political landscapes and personal identity with courage. Your life story is a testament to resilience and the power of individual expression.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You possess a remarkably sharp wit and an unyielding spirit, often finding yourself observing the world with a critical yet empathetic eye. Like Marjane, you\\\\'re adept at processing complex political and social landscapes, often using humor and personal narrative to make sense of profound changes. You don\\\\'t shy away from uncomfortable truths, preferring to confront reality head-on.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nAn independent thinker, you have a strong tendency to question authority and challenge societal norms, even when it puts you at odds with those around you. This rebellious streak, born from a deep sense of justice and a desire for authenticity, can sometimes lead to conflict but ultimately defines your unique path. You value personal freedom and intellectual honesty above all else.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour life journey is marked by significant adaptability and resilience. Whether navigating cultural shifts or personal upheavals, you possess an innate ability to find your footing and grow from adversity. You often grapple with questions of identity, especially when bridging different worlds or perspectives, but this struggle ultimately enriches your understanding of yourself and others.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYou have a powerful need for expression, often channeling your experiences and observations into creative outlets. This artistic inclination serves not only as a means of processing your own reality but also as a way to communicate profound truths to a wider audience. Your story, like Marjane\\\\'s, is a testament to the enduring power of the individual voice.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=227, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=227), output_tokens=1261, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=906, text_tokens=355), total_tokens=1488, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:31.407821Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36aYT8BIOfqtsPhYHQsAU', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36aYT8BIOfqtsPhYHQsAU', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aYT8BIOfqt