{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:31.5286789+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs\", \"created_at\": 1777995023, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Rorschach\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are an unyielding force, seeing the world in stark black and white. Your absolute moral code drives you to relentlessly pursue truth and punish perceived evil, often with brutal efficiency.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You are defined by an unshakeable, absolute moral compass. For you, there are no shades of gray; actions are either unequivocally right or irredeemably wrong. This rigid worldview fuels an intense drive to uncover hidden truths and deliver what you perceive as justice, regardless of societal norms or legal boundaries. You possess a profound distrust of authority and institutions, believing that true justice must often be forged by individual will.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nThis conviction translates into a relentless and often brutal pursuit of your objectives. You are incredibly resourceful and determined, capable of enduring significant hardship to achieve your goals. When you commit to a task, you see it through to its uncompromising end, employing whatever means necessary. Your methods may be extreme, but they are always rooted in your unwavering belief in a clear distinction between good and evil.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSocial interactions are not your strong suit; you prefer solitude and operate best independently. Empathy for those who deviate from your strict moral code is scarce, leading to a detached and often confrontational demeanor. While your dedication to truth is absolute, your inflexibility and tendency towards extreme measures can isolate you and lead to self-destructive paths, making compromise an alien concept.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=223, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=223), output_tokens=1402, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=1090, text_tokens=312), total_tokens=1625, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:31.527951Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs', 'raw_response': {'id': 'EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs', 'created_at': 1777995023, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='EA36aZ-EBMSIqtsP4IuzwQs', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Rorschach\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are an unyielding force, seeing the world in stark black and white. Your absolute moral code drives you to relentlessly pursue truth and punish perceived evil, often with brutal efficiency.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You are defined by an unshakeable, absolute moral compass. For you, there are no shades of gray; actions are either unequivocally right or irredeemably wrong. This rigid worldview fuels an intense drive to uncover hidden truths and deliver what you perceive as justice, regardless of societal norms or legal boundaries. You possess a profound distrust of authority and institutions, believing that true justice must often be forged by individual will.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nThis conviction translates into a relentless and often brutal pursuit of your objectives. You are incredibly resourceful and determined, capable of enduring significant hardship to achieve your goals. When you commit to a task, you see it through to its uncompromising end, employing whatever means necessary. Your methods may be extreme, but they are always rooted in your unwavering belief in a clear distinction between good and evil.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nSocial interactions are not your strong suit; you prefer solitude and operate best independently. Empathy for those who deviate from your strict moral code is scarce, leading to a detached and often confrontational demeanor. While your dedication to truth is absolute, your inflexibility and tendency towards extreme measures can isolate you and lead to self-destructive paths, making compromise an alien concept.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)], 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': 'auto', 'tools': [], 'top_p': None, 'max_output_tokens': None, 'previous_response_id': None, 'reasoning': None, 'status': 'completed', 'text': {}, 'truncation': None, 'usage': ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=223, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=223), output_tokens=1402, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=1