{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:36.5502816+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"Fg36afeLHNXnqtsP25WZIA\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"Fg36afeLHNXnqtsP25WZIA\", \"created_at\": 1777995030, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='Fg36afeLHNXnqtsP25WZIA', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Enid Coleslaw\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You possess a sharp wit and a keen eye for the absurdities of modern life, often expressing yourself through a cynical, yet deeply observant, lens. Your artistic sensibilities and rebellious spirit drive you to question the status quo, even as you navigate the complexities of finding your place in the world.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You are a true individual, marked by a distinctive blend of cynicism and artistic sensitivity. With a razor-sharp wit and an often-sarcastic demeanor, you observe the world around you, quick to point out its hypocrisies and banalities. This critical perspective isn\\\\'t born of malice, but rather a deep-seated intelligence and a refusal to accept things at face value. You find solace and expression in counter-culture, art, and the obscure, often feeling like an outsider looking in.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour relationships, particularly close friendships, are often complex, characterized by shared observations and a unique understanding, but also by underlying tensions and a struggle for connection. You may find yourself pushing people away or feeling misunderstood, as your authentic self can be challenging for others to grasp. Beneath the tough exterior lies a searching soul, grappling with identity, purpose, and the transition into adulthood, often feeling a profound sense of alienation.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYou have a strong aesthetic, drawn to vintage, punk, and anything that defies mainstream appeal. Your artistic inclinations are a vital outlet for your observations and frustrations, whether through drawing, writing, or simply curating your own unique style. You prefer authenticity over superficiality, even if that authenticity comes with a dose of melancholy or discomfort. Your journey is one of self-discovery, constantly questioning, creating, and trying to define what truly matters to you.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=225, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=225), output_tokens=1126, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=749, text_tokens=377), total_tokens=1351, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:36.549548Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'Fg36afeLHNXnqtsP25WZIA', 'raw_response': {'id': 'Fg36afeLHNXnqtsP25WZIA', 'created_at': 1777995030, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='messa