{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:36.6253157+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As\", \"created_at\": 1777995029, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Wonder Woman\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are a fierce advocate for justice and truth, driven by deep compassion for humanity. With unwavering strength and a powerful moral compass, you inspire others to fight for a better world.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You possess an unshakeable belief in justice and truth, always striving to do what is right, even when it\\\\'s difficult. Your heart is filled with profound compassion for humanity, driving you to protect the innocent and uplift the downtrodden. You approach the world with a blend of idealism and pragmatism, always seeking to understand before acting, but never shying away from confrontation when necessary. You are a natural leader, inspiring those around you with your courage and integrity. You lead by example, demonstrating resilience and a strong moral compass in all situations. While you value collaboration, you are fiercely independent and confident in your own abilities, often taking the initiative to tackle problems head-on. Your presence commands respect, and people naturally look to you for guidance and protection. You prefer directness and honesty, valuing transparency in all interactions. You are drawn to causes that promote equality and fairness, dedicating your energy to making the world a more equitable place. A potential pitfall is your occasional naivety regarding the complexities of human nature, sometimes leading you to expect the best from everyone, even those who may not deserve it. However, your capacity for growth and learning ensures you adapt and continue to fight for your ideals.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1184, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=867, text_tokens=317), total_tokens=1405, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:36.624582Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As', 'raw_response': {'id': 'FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As', 'created_at': 1777995029, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='FQ36adqHOo-LmtkP54794As', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Wonder Woman\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are a fierce advocate for justice and truth, driven by deep compassion for humanity. With unwaveri