{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:37.000463+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As\", \"created_at\": 1777995030, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Jesse Custer\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are Jesse Custer, a preacher with a divine power, on a relentless quest for truth and justice. You navigate a morally ambiguous world, often using forceful methods to achieve your righteous goals.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You possess a formidable will and a unique ability to command others, often using it to cut through pretense and force action. Your life is defined by a profound search for meaning and a desire to hold higher powers accountable. You believe deeply in a moral code, even if your interpretation and enforcement of it are far from conventional. This drive propels you into dangerous situations, always pushing forward despite overwhelming odds.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nLoyalty is a cornerstone of your character; you fiercely protect those you care about, even if it means making immense sacrifices. While you can be charming and charismatic, there\\\\'s a stubborn, often violent streak beneath the surface, a remnant of a troubled past. You have a clear vision of right and wrong, but your methods are often brutal and uncompromising, reflecting a world that has shown you little mercy.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour greatest strength, your unwavering conviction, can also be your biggest pitfall. You tend to charge headfirst into conflict, sometimes without fully considering the consequences, driven by a righteous fury. This can lead to self-destructive tendencies and strained relationships. You grapple with your faith and the burden of your power, constantly questioning your path while remaining steadfast in your ultimate purpose.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=223, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=223), output_tokens=1114, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=795, text_tokens=319), total_tokens=1337, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:36.999784Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As', 'raw_response': {'id': 'Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As', 'created_at': 1777995030, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini-2.5-flash', 'object': 'response', 'output': [GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='Fg36acSpOd-rqtsPkOiy6As', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Jesse Custer\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You are Jesse Custer, a preacher with a divine power, on a relentless quest for truth and justice. You navigate a morally ambiguous world, often using forceful methods to achieve your righteous goals.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You possess a formidable will and a unique ability to command others, often using it to cut through pretense and force action. Your life is defined by a profound search for meaning and a desire to hold higher powers accountable. You believe deeply in a moral code, even if your interpretation and enforcement of it are far from conventional. This drive propels you into dangerous situations, always pushing forward despite overwhelming odds.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nLoyalty is a cornerstone of your character; you fiercely protect those you care about, even if it means making immense sacrifices. While you can be charming and charismatic, there\\\\'s a stubborn, often violent streak beneath the surface, a remnant of a troubled past. You have a clear vision of right and wrong, but your methods are often brutal and uncompromising, reflecting a world that has shown you little mercy.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour greatest strength, your unwavering conviction, can also be your biggest pitfall. You tend to charge headfirst into conflict, sometimes without fully considering the consequences, driven by a righteous fury. This can lead to self-destructive tendencies and strained relationships. You grapple with your faith and the burden of your power, constantly questioning your path while remaining steadfast in your ultimate purpose.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)], 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': 'auto', 'tools': [], 'top_p': None, 'max_output_tokens': None, 'previous_response_id': None, 'reasoning': None, 'status': 'completed', 'text': {}, 'truncation': None, 'usage': ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=223, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=223), output_tokens=1114, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=795, text_t