{"TimeStamp": "2026-05-05T15:30:37.3893213+00:00", "Log": "F {\"model\": \"gemini/gemini-2.5-flash\", \"tool\": \"profile_writer\", \"trace_id\": \"257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532\", \"session_id\": \"e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab\", \"response_id\": \"Fg36af-DGamlqtsPj-D-yAs\", \"raw_response\": {\"id\": \"Fg36af-DGamlqtsPj-D-yAs\", \"created_at\": 1777995030, \"error\": null, \"incomplete_details\": null, \"instructions\": null, \"metadata\": {}, \"model\": \"gemini-2.5-flash\", \"object\": \"response\", \"output\": [\"GenericResponseOutputItem(type='message', id='Fg36af-DGamlqtsPj-D-yAs', status='completed', role='assistant', content=[OutputText(type='output_text', text='{\\\\n  \\\"name\\\": \\\"Hellboy\\\",\\\\n  \\\"short_description\\\": \\\"You\\\\'re a creature of two worlds, grappling with a powerful destiny while fiercely protecting humanity. Your gruff exterior hides a deep sense of duty and a surprisingly soft spot for the underdog.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"profile_text\\\": \\\"You embody a fascinating paradox, born of infernal origins yet choosing to stand as humanity\\\\'s most unlikely defender. Your existence is a constant negotiation between a preordained, apocalyptic destiny and your unwavering commitment to doing good, often against your own nature. This internal struggle defines much of your journey, making you a complex figure driven by a deep, if sometimes begrudging, sense of purpose.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nBeneath a formidable, often intimidating exterior lies a surprisingly down-to-earth and pragmatic individual. You tackle problems head-on, preferring direct action and a good punch over convoluted plans. Your sharp wit and sarcastic humor serve as a coping mechanism, deflecting the weight of your responsibilities and the strangeness of your everyday life. You\\\\'re not one for grand speeches, but your actions speak volumes about your resolve.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nDespite your monstrous appearance and the grim nature of your work, you possess a profound capacity for loyalty and compassion. You form deep bonds with those you trust, and you have a soft spot for the simple pleasures in life \\u2013 a stack of pancakes, a cold beer, or the quiet companionship of a stray cat. These small comforts ground you amidst the chaos and remind you of the humanity you strive to protect.\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\nYour greatest challenge often comes from within, as you constantly battle the expectations of your heritage and the temptation of a darker path. You might feel like an outsider, misunderstood by both the world you protect and the one you came from. Yet, it is precisely this struggle that fuels your heroic spirit, proving that destiny is not always fixed, and even a demon can choose to be a champion.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1295, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=889, text_tokens=406), total_tokens=1516, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:30:37.388576Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-2.5-flash', 'tool': 'profile_writer', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'Fg36af-DGamlqtsPj-D-yAs', 'raw_response': {'id': 'Fg36af-DGamlqtsPj-D-yAs', 'created_at': 1777995030, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': No