 and the temptation of a darker path. You might feel like an outsider, misunderstood by both the world you protect and the one you came from. Yet, it is precisely this struggle that fuels your heroic spirit, proving that destiny is not always fixed, and even a demon can choose to be a champion.\\\",\\\\n  \\\"image_url\\\": null\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)], 'parallel_tool_calls': False, 'temperature': 0.0, 'tool_choice': 'auto', 'tools': [], 'top_p': None, 'max_output_tokens': None, 'previous_response_id': None, 'reasoning': None, 'status': 'completed', 'text': {}, 'truncation': None, 'usage': ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=221, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=221), output_tokens=1295, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=889, text_tokens=406), total_tokens=1516, cost=None), 'user': None, 'store': None}, 'event': 'llm.raw_response.received', 'level': 'info', 'logger': 'app.services.llm_service', 'timestamp': '2026-05-05T15:30:37.388576Z'}\\\">\", \"_from_structlog\": true}"}
