ally a team and inspire others to take a stand together.\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ]\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"What is the driving force behind your most important decisions?\\\",\\\\n      \\\"options\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"A past tragedy or personal history that I am trying to rectify.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"A grand ideological vision for how the world should be.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"The simple desire to protect and provide for my inner circle.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"A search for my own identity and a place to belong.\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ]\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"How do you typically interact with established authority figures?\\\",\\\\n      \\\"options\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"I ignore them and operate entirely outside their systems.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"I openly challenge them through wit, art, or rebellion.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"I lead them by example, showing a better way to govern.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"I try to cooperate, but I often find myself at odds with their rules.\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ]\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"Which of these best describes your social presence?\\\",\\\\n      \\\"options\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Stoic and guarded; I prefer to work alone in the shadows.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Theatrical and charismatic; I use symbols to make a point.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Sarcastic and blunt; I use humor to keep people at a distance.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Approachable and earnest; I value genuine connection with others.\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ]\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\"question_text\\\": \\\"What is your preferred way to spend a quiet evening?\\\",\\\\n      \\\"options\\\": [\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Training, studying, or perfecting a difficult skill.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Engaging with high culture, literature, or philosophical debate.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Relaxing with simple comforts like a good meal or music.\\\"\\\\n        },\\\\n        {\\\\n          \\\"text\\\": \\\"Spending time with friends or playing games to unwind.\\\"\\\\n        }\\\\n      ]\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}', annotations=[])], phase=None)\"], \"parallel_tool_calls\": false, \"temperature\": 0.0, \"tool_choice\": \"auto\", \"tools\": [], \"top_p\": null, \"max_output_tokens\": null, \"previous_response_id\": null, \"reasoning\": null, \"status\": \"completed\", \"text\": {}, \"truncation\": null, \"usage\": \"ResponseAPIUsage(input_tokens=3660, input_tokens_details=InputTokensDetails(audio_tokens=None, cached_tokens=0, text_tokens=3660), output_tokens=2045, output_tokens_details=OutputTokensDetails(reasoning_tokens=1236, text_tokens=809), total_tokens=5705, cost=None)\", \"user\": null, \"store\": null}, \"event\": \"llm.raw_response.received\", \"level\": \"info\", \"logger\": \"app.services.llm_service\", \"timestamp\": \"2026-05-05T15:31:01.345802Z\", \"_record\": \"<LogRecord: app.services.llm_service, 20, /app/app/services/llm_service.py, 754, \\\"{'model': 'gemini/gemini-flash-latest', 'tool': 'question_generator', 'trace_id': '257873e3-e001-42ba-b9e4-bca1c5314532', 'session_id': 'e29276fc-8c2c-4453-995e-d2b5298429ab', 'response_id': 'KA36aYWrHN6zmtkPgYrv6Qs', 'raw_response': {'id': 'KA36aYWrHN6zmtkPgYrv6Qs', 'created_at': 1777995048, 'error': None, 'incomplete_details': None, 'instructions': None, 'metadata': {}, 'model': 'gemini